The Rorschach Mask Doctrine is a core engine for observer-dependent clarity, ambiguity resolution, narrative compression, and adversarial detection.
It turns the human tendency to “fill in the blank” into a computational diagnostic tool.

This module upgrades PantheonOS by adding:
	•	interpretive geometry
	•	symbolic safety
